abstract: Baseball Roundup; Washington Nationals defeat Philadelphia Phillies, 3-2; other MLB scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Stephen Strasburg (5-5) allowed two runs on four hits with one walk and nine strikeouts in his second solid outing since returning from the disabled list.

headline.main: Strasburg Is Strong Again for Nationals as He Makes His Way Back From Injury
